ol.li: User query is sent to RAG Service
RAG service determines which metadata from all avalable tools is likely gong to be needed by the LLM to process the query.
The shortened list of tools is sent to the LLM along with the query.
The LLM calls each tool as needed using the metadata and appropriate parameters. Note that both Method Tools and MCP tools are implemented and used.
After suitable interchange between the LLM and the tool, a response is returned to the User.
